## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **pilocarpine Salagen 1994** = first FDA M3 muscarinic agonist sicca. cevimeline Evoxac 2000 = second M3 muscarinic selective Sjögren primary. M3 muscarinic 가 양자-VQE 의 GPCR pocket fit.
2. **cyclosporine Restasis 2003 + Cequa 2018** = ocular dryness — calcineurin ophthalmic. lifitegrast Xiidra 2016 = first LFA-1 antagonist DED. perfluorohexyloctane Miebo 2023 = first FDA evaporative dry eye. ophthalmology cross-link 결정적.
3. **hydroxychloroquine** = 만성 systemic 1L Sjögren — 임상 anchor. methotrexate + corticosteroid + cyclophosphamide = systemic extraglandular bridge.
4. **rituximab anti-CD20 off-label** = refractory Sjögren — Phase 3 RCT (TRACTISS / TEARS) negative on primary endpoint 임에도 임상 사용 지속. paradigm tension.
5. **ianalumab Novartis VAY736 BAFF-R mAb Phase 3** = first BAFF-R mAb Sjögren — B-cell depletion + BAFF-R 차단 dual mechanism. quantum-VQE 의 BAFF-R extracellular domain pocket fit.
6. **iscalimab Novartis CFZ533 CD40 mAb Phase 3** = first CD40 mAb Sjögren. CD40-CD40L co-stimulation 차단 — non-depleting + thrombosis-safer (CD40L mAb 의 1990s 부작용 회피).
7. **dazodalibep CD40L pathway Phase 2/3** = ICOSL/CD40L Fc-fusion — CD40L 직접 차단 next-gen.
8. **iberdomide BMS CRBN modulator** = Sjögren research extension (cross-sle_lupus_specific). Cereblon E3 ligase substrate degradation paradigm.
9. **nipocalimab FcRn** = Sjögren research extension (cross-myasthenia_specific). IgG recycling 차단 — autoantibody 감소 paradigm.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, Sjögren primary + secondary 임상 의미 한정. K-Sjögren + 식약처 framework + 산정특례 cross-link 만 정책 layer.

